subSubSection.paragraph:
Genetic distances.
Following tradition, we use Kimura 2-parameter (K2P) genetic distances (

Hebert 
et al.
, 2003

), but see (
Srivathsan & Meier, 2012
) for criticism. Distances were calculated in PAUP* ver. 4.0a (build 158) (
Swofford, 2016
) using the default settings.
